snippet: LEAD: A hitch has emerged that might derail plans for an early Presidential primary in California, despite the support of both national political parties and the agreement of California's legislative leadership and Gov. George Deukmejian....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: A hitch has emerged that might derail plans for an early Presidential primary in California, despite the support of both national political parties and the agreement of California's legislative leadership and Gov. George Deukmejian.

headline.main: California Measure For Earlier Primary Is Raising Questions
